# r1 daemon sidecar binaries are populated by
# desktop/scripts/copy-r1-binaries.sh ahead of `cargo tauri build`
# (per spec desktop-cortex-augmentation §2). They MUST NOT be tracked
# in git: each is a multi-MB build artefact whose canonical source is
# the per-triple `target/<triple>/release/r1` produced by `go build`
# for that target.
*
!.gitignore
